  "time_ut": 1661229418,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dda \u0db6\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person who stole goods from the Prime Minister's office was caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police Headquarters says that yesterday (22nd) a suspect was arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department for attacking the Prime Minister's office and its property, causing damage and stealing the property.",
        "A 33-year-old man, a resident of Talangama Koswatta area, has been arrested."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
